                  </h2>
                  <p className="max-w-2xl mb-6 text-lg text-white/80">
                    Ready to continue your learning journey? You have 3 study sessions scheduled today.
                  </p>

                  {/* Quick Action Buttons */}
                  <div className="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
